318.1	James_Hansen	James Hansen	James E. Hansen (born March 29, 1941) heads the NASA Goddard Institute for Space Studies in New York City, a part of the Goddard Space Flight Center in Greenbelt, Maryland. He has held this position since 1981. He is also an adjunct professor in the Department of Earth and Environmental Sciences at Columbia University.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/James_E_Hansen.jpg/220px-James_E_Hansen.jpg
